{"tid":916630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"選舉激情過後想洩慾　別學這對男女危險車震","createTime":"2018-11-26T00:06:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T11:00:52.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d768ccba6d6febb78ef32c9588f2ba8928e7e720","tid":916630,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T00:06:45.000Z","msg":"台灣九合一選舉落幕，勝負也已揭曉，相信有些民眾在選舉激情過後想要發洩一下，但千萬別學這對男女，無視交通規則與安全，竟然進行危險車震。<br />\n據英國《每日郵報》報導，美國堪薩斯州的一名駕駛，在公路上拍到在他身旁呼嘯而過的一輛車子，車內的男駕駛身上，坐著一名女子，這名男子一邊開車，就一邊與女子做愛。只見女子上上下下不間斷，男子抓著女子的頭，陶醉在絕頂升天的快感中，無視交通安全，而男子還一度對攝影鏡頭比中指。<br />\n這段影片從周二開始被流傳，相信這段車震並未造成任何事故與傷亡，這對男女也未遭到警方逮捕。但就有網友說，如果當時男子被交通警察抓到，「相信我，那個罰金絕對會讓他永生難忘」。還有網友大罵：「這真的超級不負責任、超危險！」（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181126/640_ce30ee9fe6fac34b10026393baba491c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181126%2F640_ce30ee9fe6fac34b10026393baba491c.jpg&h=9a69312e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181126/1472474/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181126%2F1472474%2F&d=dguNJB8dEEVqf6lFflmCrNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=2e60bb3f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181126%2F1472474%2F&h=2b29384d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181126/1472474/</a>"},{"pid":"828e143350ec0d4ec948a466a1c0bdf57e032798","tid":916630,"uid":100961,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T00:08:26.000Z","msg":"又係風化精英<span style=\"color: red;\">施旖婕</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a5bf756f43b7a92eda418c9ff68011253310b31","tid":916630,"uid":77196,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime